---
// Wrapper: lays out child <Stat /> items as a row of big numbers.
---

<div class="stats-band"><slot /></div>

<style>
  .stats-band {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.4rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 1.4rem 1.2rem;
    border-block: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--muted) 40%, transparent);
  }
</style>
